'''Enlightenment''' is a light-weight and eye-candy desktop environment.

== Installation  ==
Recommended are the following local USE flags as sane default to be able to auto mount removable devices, etc.:
{{File|/etc/portage/package.use||<pre>
media-libs/evas fontconfig
dev-libs/ecore evas fbcon curl
media-libs/edje cache vim-syntax
x11-wm/enlightenment udev ukit
x11-libs/elementary -quicklaunch thumbnails weather xdg
x11-themes/efennhit gtk
</pre>}}

If you don't want to undergo the painful manual installation of each package, you'd better use sets. One can add these two sets to {{Path|/etc/portage/sets/}} to ease merging and rebuilding the packages:
